The paper deals with the problem of transfer learning in reinforcement learning, which is a subfield of machine learning. The proposed approach involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the category of deep learning. Therefore, cs.LG (Machine Learning) is the most likely sub-category. The paper also deals with the problem of learning embeddings, which is a common theme in natural language processing (NLP) and computer vision (CV), hence cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence), cs.CV (Computer Vision), and cs.CL (Computation and Language) are also likely sub-categories. Finally, the paper involves experiments on GridWorld and Thor, which are environments used in robotics, hence cs.RO (Robotics) is also a possible sub-category.
